      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NITROUS (4) goes very well this course and distance starting five times for two wins and two minors. Was out of the placings last time (43.97) at this track in a OPEN, finishing fifth and beaten 15 lengths. Looks the one to beat with even luck. MEMORIES OF ROSE (1) ran fifth in a Grade 5 last time, copping a check in the run and finishing 13 lengths from the winner over 531m at Gawler. Has three wins from Box 1. Must include in calculations. MOSCOW CHICK (6) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 5.5 lengths into third (30.49) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 4/5 over 530m. Expected to be in this for a long way. CANYA VIVI (3) was in the money last start at this track and distance - poses a threat again.",
